---

## ðŸ’¡ Entry Tips
- Start with AWS or Azure free labs and certification paths
- Learn to secure IAM, S3 buckets, and serverless resources
- Use Terraform and GitHub Actions to explore automation
- Join cloud and DevSecOps communities (CloudSecCollective, Reddit, Discord)

